edu.brown.cs.gk16

Class Vertex<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.gk16.Vertex<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - object to be contained in the vertex
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Actor

    public class Vertex<V>
extends Object
    The representation of a graph vertex. It stores an element, a unique vertex number, a distance value, and the incident edges (edges going away).

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Vertex(V v, int number)
      Takes in the vertex element (can be null) and a number - this number should be unique.
